Dialogue: 5,0:00:01.97,0:00:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is a national holiday, Mother's Day.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:05.58,0:00:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you love or hate your mom,\Nwhether you get along with her or not,
Dialogue: 5,0:00:11.02,0:00:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you were given Mother's Day to enjoy as a Japanese person.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:17.70,0:00:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't come to this park for any particular reason.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:22.54,0:00:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I arrived here by just riding my mountain bike randomly,
Dialogue: 5,0:00:26.75,0:00:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,going wherever my feet carried me.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:31.63,0:00:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, as the only one in a park on a Sunday,
Dialogue: 5,0:00:35.50,0:00:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it felt like I was the only one in the world.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:40.43,0:00:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it's an exaggeration,
Dialogue: 5,0:00:43.35,0:00:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it felt as if perhaps the park belonged to me.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:48.36,0:00:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if it would be perfectly all right to never go back home.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:51.15,0:00:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:53.86,0:00:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's only me.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:55.95,0:00:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm alone.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:09.16,0:01:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alone again?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:11.04,0:01:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:13.08,0:01:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna be like that{\fscx250}-{\fscx100}!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:14.51,0:01:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna be like that, bro!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:33.73,0:01:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.  Well, well.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:36.14,0:01:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought someone left a dead dog here.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:38.52,0:01:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it turns out it's just you, Araragi-kun.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:42.97,0:01:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?  I was just saying hello.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:45.49,0:01:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a joke.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:46.70,0:01:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, uh.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:48.26,0:01:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, then?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:49.49,0:01:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Araragi-kun, you little boy.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:50.97,0:01:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you just fascinated by my charming street clothes?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:54.21,0:01:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A moment of bliss?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:56.71,0:01:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That may have just been a bad pun,
Dialogue: 5,0:01:58.34,0:02:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I really was fascinated.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:00.76,0:02:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, the second kanji in\N"fascinating" is an amazing kanji, isn't it?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:04.72,0:02:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:05.77,0:02:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second kanji is written with the grass radical over a bath.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:08.54,0:02:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, its sensitivity is a step beyond the bright and happy "moe" that uses the grass radical.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:13.27,0:02:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm waiting for it to be introduced and used in the next generation.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:17.82,0:02:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can have "maid fascination" or "cat ears fascination". {note this segment}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:22.53,0:02:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:26.81,0:02:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just surprised because those clothes give a completely different impression than what I saw you in before.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:30.88,0:02:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:32.55,0:02:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:33.90,0:02:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's because I was wearing mellower clothes then.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:36.88,0:02:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:39.60,0:02:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, I bought this whole outfit yesterday.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:44.67,0:02:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm happy.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:46.22,0:02:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted you to see these clothes first if possible, Araragi-kun.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:52.19,0:02:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if you wanted to show them to me first...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:55.81,0:02:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uh...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:57.14,0:02:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes it sound like a stroke of luck or an honor.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:00.36,0:03:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to show you them, Araragi-kun.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:02.95,0:03:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted you to see them.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:04.66,0:03:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The nuance is completely different.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:11.17,0:03:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Araragi-kun.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:13.06,0:03:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:15.78,0:03:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little touring.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:18.15,0:03:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like going out on my bike.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:20.20,0:03:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I found this park, so I figured I'd take a rest.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:24.00,0:03:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you, Senjougahara?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:25.36,0:03:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you come here often?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:27.01,0:03:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This used to be my place.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:30.18,0:03:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Your place"?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:31.60,0:03:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, you said you used to live around here.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:35.01,0:03:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:38.10,0:03:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then it all changed.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:40.71,0:03:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm too sentimental about it, but...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:45.11,0:03:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, seeing how where I used to live has changed makes my motivation slip away.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:52.94,0:03:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it unavoidable?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:55.84,0:03:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.  It's unavoidable.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:59.96,0:04:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Araragi-kun.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:01.72,0:04:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't care if I sit next to you, do you?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:04.05,0:04:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next to me?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:04.97,0:04:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to discuss with you.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:08.14,0:04:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:09.25,0:04:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having a whole bench to myself made me feel a little uneasy.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:14.49,0:04:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:15.40,0:04:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll go right ahead.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:23.15,0:04:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd try thanking you again for these recent events.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:27.99,0:04:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really care about that.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:31.70,0:04:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go thank Oshino instead.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:33.66,0:04:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be more than enough.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:36.54,0:04:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to pay Oshino the fee.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:40.34,0:04:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to thank you in a different way than Oshino.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:44.91,0:04:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uh.  Stop thinking that you owe me something.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:51.19,0:04:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to make it tough to get along with you.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:55.02,0:04:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To get along, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:58.02,0:04:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Araragi-kun.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:00.22,0:05:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I think of you as someone dear?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:06.07,0:05:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:07.57,0:05:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're not the type of person who makes friends easily, are you?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:12.66,0:05:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was like that until last year,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:14.66,0:05:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I had a paradigm shift over spring break.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you, Senjougahara?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:22.05,0:05:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was like that until just recently.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:24.70,0:05:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More specifically, until I met you.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:28.34,0:05:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's she saying?!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:29.82,0:05:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this situation?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:31.47,0:05:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This situation... It's like she's about to tell me she loves me.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:36.28,0:05:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I mean to say, Araragi-kun.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:38.35,0:05:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that no matter what you say, I have to pay you back.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:43.70,0:05:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once that's over,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:46.40,0:05:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be able to become friends on an even footing.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:51.33,0:05:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:52.95,0:05:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:54.91,0:05:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Araragi-kun, perhaps there's something you want me to do?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:59.58,0:06:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just this once, I'll do anything.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:02.87,0:06:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:03.84,0:06:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything at all.  Just this once, I'll fulfill whatever your wish is.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:08.83,0:06:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's world conquest, or eternal life, or to defeat the Saiyans that are coming to earth.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:13.70,0:06:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you're more powerful than Shen Long?!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:17.27,0:06:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:18.31,0:06:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She went along with it.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:20.18,0:06:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to be honest, it's easier for me to help with something more personal.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:25.97,0:06:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it's simpler.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:27.11,0:06:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure is.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:29.15,0:06:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, anything's okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:31.07,0:06:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like saying you want me to end all my sentences with "nyu" for a week.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:34.65,0:06:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or that you want me not to wear underwear to school for a week.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:39.06,0:06:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or that you want me to wake you up every morning for a week, wearing nothing but an apron.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:42.88,0:06:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or that you want me to help out with colon cleansing for a week.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:46.83,0:06:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to have plenty of kinks.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.44,0:06:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'm that kind of a pervert!?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:53.84,0:06:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that really rude?!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:56.10,0:06:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uh, sorry,
Dialogue: 5,0:06:58.71,0:07:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm not sure if I can go along with them for a lifetime.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:04.10,0:07:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!  Wrong, wrong, wrong!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:06.07,0:07:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not pissed off because you think I'm less of a perv!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:11.28,0:07:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:13.18,0:07:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I may suggest, I recommend my waking you up every morning wearing nothing but an apron.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:19.59,0:07:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I can cook you breakfast.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:22.75,0:07:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a man's fantasy to watch that from behind?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:26.84,0:07:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Senjougahara.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:29.12,0:07:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we make that deal,
Dialogue: 5,0:07:32.01,0:07:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think we'll be able to think of each other as just friends after.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:36.85,0:07:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my.  Now that you mention it, it does seem like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:40.03,0:07:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.  Then nothing sexual.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:44.19,0:07:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess I figured you wouldn't want anything sexual.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:50.64,0:07:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you do have faith in me.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:52.97,0:07:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you're a virgin.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:54.60,0:07:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's said that before.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:56.89,0:08:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Virgins aren't picky, so it's easy on the other person.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:00.08,0:08:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Senjougahara.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:02.54,0:08:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you've done that much either.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:04.96,0:08:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?  I'm plenty experienced.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:07.63,0:08:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:08.84,0:08:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do it all the time.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:12.03,0:08:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, if that were really true, Senjougahara,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:18.68,0:08:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what would you gain by telling me?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:22.06,0:08:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. I'll correct myself.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:26.15,0:08:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no experience.  I'm a virgin.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:30.03,0:08:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, the only kind of girl who would talk to an unappealing virgin like you
Dialogue: 5,0:08:35.11,0:08:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are late-bloomer crazy virgins like me!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:41.83,0:08:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,We've kind of gotten onto a tangent,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:43.78,0:08:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,but is there anything you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:46.15,0:08:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,To put it more simply, maybe something you're troubled by?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:49.70,0:08:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,Something that I'm troubled by...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:51.68,0:08:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,I don't really have a way with words, so I can't say it,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:54.64,0:08:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,but I really do want to help you.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:00.22,0:09:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess, if I have to say it...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:02.97,0:09:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:04.82,0:09:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to me about it.  If you just talk about it, it'll be easier. I guess.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:10.00,0:09:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:11.67,0:09:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a fight with my little sister.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:13.82,0:09:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really help you with that.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:17.99,0:09:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll listen to the whole thing just in case.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:20.80,0:09:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Just in case"...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:23.58,0:09:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So which sister did you fight with?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:26.36,0:09:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you do have two of them.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:30.57,0:09:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:32.55,0:09:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The older of the two.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:34.92,0:09:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But really, it's a problem with both of them.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:37.40,0:09:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter when, where, or what they're doing, they're always asking the five Ws and one H.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:41.64,0:09:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because they hang out together so much.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:44.33,0:09:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they are the Tsuganoki Second Junior High Fire Sisters.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:47.35,0:09:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You even know their nickname?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:49.56,0:09:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, today's Mother's Day, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:53.12,0:09:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, it is.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:55.46,0:09:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're both attached to Mom.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:58.50,0:10:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Mom fusses over them like a mother cat over kittens.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:02.67,0:10:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:03.29,0:10:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:04.63,0:10:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a bad son, it's like your own house isn't your home today on Mother's Day.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:12.60,0:10:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty much.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:15.80,0:10:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got up early in the morning so I could sneak out of the house.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:18.89,0:10:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sister caught me getting on my bike.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:22.96,0:10:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we argued.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:24.29,0:10:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Argued?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:25.30,0:10:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said that, as my sister, she wanted me to stay and celebrate Mother's Day together.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:29.68,0:10:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, hey, I can't do that.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:33.40,0:10:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna be like that, bro{\fscx250}-{\fscx100}!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:35.21,0:10:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're like that, no matter how much time passes{\fscx250}-{\fscx100}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:41.74,0:10:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, basically.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:43.24,0:10:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even celebrate on Mother's Day,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:45.90,0:10:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and get pissed off at what my four years younger sister says.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:50.89,0:10:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I call smallness as a human being,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:54.68,0:10:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much I'm irritated by it, I can't do anything about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:58.65,0:11:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a complex issue.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:00.33,0:11:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not complex, just stunted.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:03.36,0:11:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because as a human being I'm small, or something.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:06.28,0:11:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even still, when I think that I'm gonna have to apologize to my sister,
Dialogue: 5,0:11:09.91,0:11:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely don't wanna go home.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:12.43,0:11:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to go home?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:16.42,0:11:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but there's nothing I'm capable of doing about your smallness as a human being.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:22.11,0:11:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, at least put some effort in.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:23.86,0:11:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, but there's nothing I'm capable of doing about your smallness as a human being.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:30.75,0:11:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty boring, huh.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:33.71,0:11:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My worries are this tiny.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:36.08,0:11:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate it.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:40.05,0:11:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiny.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:41.23,0:11:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can call it dull if you want.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:43.38,0:11:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the dullness of only ever pulling "a little luck" at omikuji.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:48.38,0:11:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't deny your charm, Araragi-kun.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:51.24,0:11:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charm?  My charm is like only ever pulling "a little luck"?!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:55.73,0:11:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was joking.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:57.06,0:12:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Araragi-kun, your dullness isn't like pulling "a little luck".
Dialogue: 5,0:12:02.67,0:12:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to say it's like pulling "bad luck"?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:05.12,0:12:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my.  Isn't that amazing?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:07.90,0:12:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or shall I say, something great?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:10.24,0:12:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Araragi-kun, your dullness...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:15.50,0:12:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like pulling "great luck", but when you read the contents, it's not all that good.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:21.56,0:12:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that kind of dullness.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:23.44,0:12:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:24.89,0:12:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But little sisters are there to be loved.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:29.30,0:12:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We do nothing but fight.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:31.79,0:12:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must be eyesores, rather than cute.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:34.78,0:12:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like they're eyesores either!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:37.06,0:12:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe you're someone who shows your love in reverse.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:40.28,0:12:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect you to be into incest.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:43.36,0:12:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:44.78,0:12:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liking little sisters is a fantasy of guys who don't have any.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:48.87,0:12:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're not into incest.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:52.02,0:12:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not interested in your real little sisters.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:54.79,0:12:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I ever would be!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:56.29,0:12:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.  Araragi-kun, you look like you'd be into soro.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:59.23,0:13:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Into soro?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:00.32,0:13:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An abbreviation of "sororate marriage".
Dialogue: 5,0:13:02.09,0:13:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like levirate marriage, but for sisters.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:03.94,0:13:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's where, when your wife dies, you marry her sister.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:10.35,0:13:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think I'd do that sororate thing?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:13.41,0:13:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For you, Araragi-kun, it'd be her little sister rather than her big sister.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:16.60,0:13:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First your wife's sister would call you "big bro", and then you'd marry her.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:23.32,0:13:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after marrying, she'd still call you "big bro".
Dialogue: 5,0:13:26.47,0:13:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, by the proper meaning, you'd become a real{\fscx250}-{\fscx100}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:29.66,0:13:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that mean I'd have killed my first wife?!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:32.33,0:13:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're into soro.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:34.47,0:13:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, just say I'm into incest!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:36.92,0:13:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you said you wouldn't want your real sister.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:40.05,0:13:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want my sister-in-law either!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:42.30,0:13:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what if you came to like someone you took as a lover out of a sense of duty?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:45.25,0:13:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's{\fscx250}-{\fscx100}!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:47.60,0:13:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can get a lover out of duty?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:50.38,0:13:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are small to be shocked by mild jokes like this.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:54.68,0:13:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your words aren't mild!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:56.69,0:13:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was testing you.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:59.07,0:14:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I being tested?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:01.35,0:14:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait, you weren't being serious?!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:04.94,0:14:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I get serious, I transform.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:07.83,0:14:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Transform?!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:09.15,0:14:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome, I wanna see!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:11.05,0:14:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a big reaction for a small human being.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:15.16,0:14:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter how small of a human being you are, I'm never gonna desert you.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:20.56,0:14:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll follow along with your smallness as a human being.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:23.84,0:14:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a pretty strange way of putting it.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:26.21,0:14:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So is their anything troubling you besides your smallness as a human?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:31.55,0:14:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of abuse am I in for now?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:34.72,0:14:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a wonderfully large tolerance.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:37.06,0:14:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't overdo it with the flattery!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:38.98,0:14:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there anything?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:41.03,0:14:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe helping you study.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:43.23,0:14:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've given up on that.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:45.19,0:14:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I graduate, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:46.99,0:14:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, helping you graduate.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:48.99,0:14:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do that fine myself!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:50.91,0:14:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you want to do it yourself?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:52.87,0:14:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to pick a fight?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:55.33,0:14:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:58.62,0:15:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe you want a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:05.15,0:15:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I say I do...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:07.97,0:15:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you do?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:10.19,0:15:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:12.46,0:15:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:17.31,0:15:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:23.28,0:15:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:24.09,0:15:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get me a can of juice or something next time.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:26.75,0:15:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do that and we're even.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:29.41,0:15:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:31.03,0:15:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're unselfish, aren't you.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:32.63,0:15:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really do have large tolerance.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:41.46,0:15:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw that girl before.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:44.89,0:15:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Senjougahara.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:46.93,0:15:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you pronounce what's written on that grade-schooler's backpack?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:52.38,0:15:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:55.04,0:15:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't normally read at this range?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:57.72,0:16:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, there's single digit kanji numbers, eight and nine, and a temple.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:01.81,0:16:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So "Hachi-kyu-dera" all in a row.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:04.33,0:16:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Hachikuji, isn't it?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:06.44,0:16:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hachikuji?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:07.72,0:16:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's Hachikuji Mayoi?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:13.25,0:16:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how I look at it, she isn't the type that likes kids.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:18.01,0:16:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, mind waiting here for a minute?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:20.98,0:16:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, but where are you going?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:24.29,0:16:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go talk to that grade-schooler.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:26.69,0:16:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it a rest.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:28.16,0:16:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just gonna get shot down.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:30.24,0:16:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, she really has no problem being a bitch.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:34.97,0:16:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's up?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:36.45,0:16:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lost?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:43.19,0:16:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk to me.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:45.36,0:16:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:48.98,0:16:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:50.31,0:16:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:51.76,0:16:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got shot down.  In flames.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:56.16,0:16:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna try again!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:57.70,0:17:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what are you doing, and where are you going?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:00.38,0:17:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch and you'll see!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:07.38,0:17:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:09.90,0:17:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you lost?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:11.33,0:17:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you want to go?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:13.82,0:17:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you let me see that note?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:17.14,0:17:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:18.84,0:17:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:22.36,0:17:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, did something happen?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:24.89,0:17:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She ignored me...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:26.26,0:17:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got shunned by a grade-school girl.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:29.71,0:17:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time I'm really going for it!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:32.17,0:17:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand what you're doing or what you want to do.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:37.56,0:17:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:46.39,0:17:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:48.14,0:17:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I've finally got your attention.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:50.09,0:17:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can get anyone's attention by smacking them from behind!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:53.05,0:17:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you look troubled, so I thought I could help you out.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:58.47,0:18:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing that someone who'd smack a grade schooler in the head could ever help with!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:04.64,0:18:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:06.35,0:18:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:08.75,0:18:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...  My name is Araragi Koyomi.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:12.61,0:18:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koyomi?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:14.07,0:18:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like a girl's name.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:16.07,0:18:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eww, it's girly!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:17.77,0:18:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:20.14,0:18:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's your name?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:22.78,0:18:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hachikuji Mayoi.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:24.93,0:18:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Hachikuji Mayoi!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:27.58,0:18:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the precious name that Mom and Dad gave me!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:30.75,0:18:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, stop talking to me!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:33.27,0:18:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:35.35,0:18:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?  I'm not going to hurt you anymore.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:39.86,0:18:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the most harmless man in town!  I wouldn't hurt man or beast!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:46.56,0:18:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.  I'll let down my guard.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:49.27,0:18:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:50.90,0:18:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Mr. Man-Beast.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:52.31,0:18:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Man-Beast?!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:53.12,0:18:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:55.28,0:18:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You yelled at me!  You're scary!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:57.74,0:19:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for yelling.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:00.25,0:19:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But "Mr. Man-Beast" is mean!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:02.31,0:19:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone would yell!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:04.59,0:19:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what should I call you?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:06.79,0:19:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not just my name?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:09.00,0:19:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Araragi-san.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:11.68,0:19:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By name is great!  The best!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:13.92,0:19:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you, Araragi-san.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:18.47,0:19:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and go somewhere else!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:20.98,0:19:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, aren't you lost?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:23.63,0:19:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm perfectly fine in this situation!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:27.06,0:19:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being so stubborn!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:28.65,0:19:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not stubborn at all!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:30.17,0:19:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:31.71,0:19:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:38.04,0:19:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got caught!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:53.00,0:19:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an idiot.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:55.24,0:19:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A grade-schooler picking a fight with a high-schooler!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:01.97,0:20:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There stood a high school boy who had seriously taken on a grade-school girl, seriously fought her,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:05.25,0:20:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,seriously won with a judo throw, and seriously felt proud of himself.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:12.69,0:20:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that's me.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:18.82,0:20:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Araragi-kun.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:23.07,0:20:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me explain myself.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:25.50,0:20:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go right ahead.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:27.70,0:20:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we should let bygones be bygones.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:30.83,0:20:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks like she's lost.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:33.33,0:20:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking we could help.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:39.52,0:20:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:41.38,0:20:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:43.23,0:20:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand the situation.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:46.24,0:20:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right, Senjougahara.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:48.20,0:20:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I asked about an address around here, you'd kinda know it, right? {note-jp addressing}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:52.63,0:20:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:54.20,0:20:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess as much as anyone.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:55.94,0:20:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hachikuji.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:57.79,0:21:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you show this girl the note you were carrying before?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:02.30,0:21:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a dream that I was abused by a heinous high school boy.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:07.88,0:21:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must've been a false dream.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:09.72,0:21:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.  A false dream.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:17.24,0:21:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?  Go ahead and take it.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:20.05,0:21:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, I don't even want to touch you.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:23.89,0:21:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just to take a note!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:26.26,0:21:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to touch anything you've touched.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:29.84,0:21:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I get it.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:32.04,0:21:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about I read it to you?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:33.85,0:21:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:36.49,0:21:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know where it is?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:38.57,0:21:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know that address.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:40.19,0:21:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:41.64,0:21:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't pinpoint it, but if we head over there, I'll be able to get it by feeling.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:47.66,0:21:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, shall we go?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:50.26,0:21:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Hachikuji!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:53.00,0:21:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where to?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:54.49,0:21:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, the address on this note.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:56.70,0:21:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl should know where it is. We'll guide you there.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:00.04,0:22:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that great?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:02.93,0:22:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll guide me there?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:05.50,0:22:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you lost?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:08.80,0:22:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm lost.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:11.18,0:22:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a lost snail.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:14.19,0:22:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snail?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:15.60,0:22:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I...
Dialogue: 5,0:22:19.65,0:22:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:55.67,0:23:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Karen!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:56.35,0:23:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Tsukihi!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:57.15,0:23:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for the preview quiz!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:57.70,0:23:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiz!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:58.15,0:24:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're talking about twin stars in the Zodiac{\fscx250}-{\fscx100}
Dialogue: 5,0:24:00.08,0:24:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be talking about Gemini!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:00.74,0:24:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Pisces is twins.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:02.49,0:24:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pisces!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:03.15,0:24:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pisces!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:04.16,0:24:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode, Mayoi Snail, part 2.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:05.99,0:24:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe they aren't twins.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:07.45,0:24:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like us.
